OL,3,CChristmas charity flight gives
OL,4,Cbereaved children 'special' memories
OL,6,FAlmost 200 people including bereaved
OL,7,Fchildren and those with life-limiting
OL,8,Fconditions, as well as their families,
OL,9,Fhave been treated to a memorable
OL,10,Fflight with Father Christmas.
OL,12,FBristol Airport teamed up with airline
OL,13,FJet2 to take the children on a special
OL,14,Fone-hour flight where they could play
OL,15,Fgames and meet Santa Claus.
OL,17,FThe Santa Flight has been a festive
OL,18,Ftradition for almost 30 years, but
OL,19,Fit's the first time it's taken place
OL,20,Fsince 2019.
