OL,3,CChristmas charity flight gives
OL,4,Cbereaved children 'special' memories
OL,6,F"It means that we can all make
OL,7,Fmemories together," said Katie Day,
OL,8,Fwho was travelling with her family
OL,9,Fafter Charlton Farm Hospice nominated
OL,10,Fher 14-year-old son Samuel.
OL,12,F"The girls have never been on a plane
OL,13,Fbefore so we'll be able to go up
OL,14,Ftogether and have a wonderful time as
OL,15,Fa family," she said.
OL,17,FHer husband, Mr Day, added: "It
OL,18,Fdoesn't happen very often that we can
OL,19,Fall be together, so that is really
OL,20,Fgood."
