OL,3,CChristmas charity flight gives
OL,4,Cbereaved children 'special' memories
OL,6,F"It's a lovely opportunity to get out
OL,7,Fand experience all of this," said Mr
OL,8,FHall, whose son Joshua died after
OL,9,Fbeing stabbed in 2021.
OL,11,FHe was travelling with Joshua's
OL,12,Fbrother, Eli, and said it's "great to
OL,13,Fbe able to create some lovely memories
OL,14,Fin what can be a very poignant time of
OL,15,Fyear."
OL,17,FAnother parent, Sally Watts, who was
OL,18,Ftravelling with her son Toby, said the
OL,19,Fflight was a positive experience given
OL,20,Fthe "tragic year" they've endured.
