OL,3,CChristmas charity flight gives
OL,4,Cbereaved children 'special' memories
OL,6,FShe said: "We've had a lot of death in
OL,7,Four family and tragic loss so just to
OL,8,Fhave a nice day out is exciting, and
OL,9,Fit's a lot to have those feelings back
OL,10,Fin your life."
OL,12,FSome of the charities that nominated
OL,13,Ffamilies include the Great Western Air
OL,14,FAmbulance Charity, Children's Hospice
OL,15,FSouth West, Weston Hospice and the
OL,16,FBritish Heart Foundation.
