OL,6,FTracy Comer, Community Relations
OL,7,FManager at Bristol Airport said: "This
OL,8,Fis such a special day for everyone
OL,9,Finvolved and it's wonderful to be
OL,10,Foffering some very brave children a
OL,11,Fmoment of fun this Christmas time and
OL,12,Ffor them to be able to make special
OL,13,Fmemories with their families and
OL,14,Fschool friends."
